Parasoft Annotations

  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    WorkItem.Type
    A specific type of development artifact in an external requirements management system.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    WorkItem
    A WorkItem annotation allows you to associate test cases with development artifacts defined in an external requirements management system.
    WorkItem.List
    Specifies multiple WorkItem annotations for the same test case.
